# ── Datasets: keep only a minimal `garden` for CI; ignore all other scenes ──
# (datasets/*/ already covers db, tandt, lund, every mipnerf360 scene, etc. —
#  no need to list them individually.)
datasets/*/
!datasets/mipnerf360/
datasets/mipnerf360/*/
!datasets/mipnerf360/garden/
# within the kept garden, drop the bulky pre-downscaled images + COLMAP extras
datasets/mipnerf360/garden/images_*
datasets/mipnerf360/garden/poses_bounds.npy
datasets/*.txt
